gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

After that I went to Dyaal, came upon a forest and one river;
There was sitting the two women of Baeu, found peace and joy there.

Here is the translation:

There they stayed for many days, then those great sages; 
They came, a saint arrived, and gathered with all paramahamsas.

Here is the translation:

He got stuck in love, his heart became a sweet pudding; 
If I don't get what I desire in life, then that very day I'll give up eating for seven days.

Here is the translation:

He came to see him then you were jealous, not sitting with Hari-guna being jealous; 
This was said and Saint went away, then Shri-Hari came to city.
